Entry.JapaneseText: ミリッツァって、 <Blue>四星<White>の紅一点なんだよネ？
Entry.EnglishText: Militsa is the only girl in the Four Stars, isn't she?

Entry.JapaneseText: ほう、じゃあモテモテだ！
Entry.EnglishText: Oho, she must be pretty popular with the guys then!

Entry.JapaneseText: でも、他のメンバーは サレとトーマとワルトゥだヨ？
Entry.EnglishText: But aren't the other members Saleh, Tohma, and Walto?
That's a bit of a pickle...
